data.description: Welcome to your future home located in the McIntyre Neighborhood! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence features a cozy living space with wood flooring that adds a touch of warmth, creating a welcoming space. The kitchen boasts a functional design with an open concept dining area. Venture upstairs to discover three well-appointed bedrooms including a primary bedroom, complete with its own ensuite bathroom, offering a retreat for rest and relaxation. The added convenience of the one-car garage provides secure parking as well as additional storage space. Enjoy the added convenience of the community pool, close proximity to several shopping venues including Northlake Mall, various restaurants and easy access to major thoroughfares such as I-77 and I-485.  Schedule your showing today and make this wonderful property your own. Act quickly as this home is priced to sell!
